        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">sometimes thats the dice, but a good way to avoid it is to find yer mod, stay as far back as you can but still hit it with snare, snare it and while its running at you fear it..now land your dots and have pet beat on it while you keep your distance. if fear breaks you should have plenty of time to re-apply it and stay high and dry in the mean time. Btw, if the mob resists your first snare, send pet to tank him while you resnare. best of luck ;)</P><P>~52 Heretic of Saryrn~ "I do things and other good stuff"<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
